OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777558269
OL,3,C'Dodgy shops' surge across UK as vape
OL,4,Cand convenience stores tied to crime
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FSo-called 'dodgy shops' have spread
OL,8,Frapidly across UK high streets, as
OL,9,Fwell as complex criminal networks that
OL,10,Funderpinned them, according to Trading
OL,11,FStandards.
OL,13,FA report by the organisation found
OL,14,Fthat organised crime groups are linked
OL,15,Fto as many as half of vape and
OL,16,Fconvenience stores, and a quarter of
OL,17,Ffast food takeaways in some areas of
OL,18,Fthe country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777558269
OL,3,C'Dodgy shops' surge across UK as vape
OL,4,Cand convenience stores tied to crime
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FUp to a third of American candy stores
OL,8,Fin specific areas are also suspected
OL,9,Fof being a front for criminal
OL,10,Factivity, the organisation's Hidden In
OL,11,FPlain Sight report said.
OL,13,FIt has published a map of high streets
OL,14,Facross the UK for dodgy shops, along
OL,15,Fwith the 10 towns and cities perceived
OL,16,Fby its officers to be hot spots for
OL,17,FOCGs, with Birmingham, Liverpool and
OL,18,FLondon filling the top three spots.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777558269
OL,3,C'Dodgy shops' surge across UK as vape
OL,4,Cand convenience stores tied to crime
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FA survey by Trading Standards found
OL,8,Fthat 97% of its officers are aware of
OL,9,Fsuspected organised crime groups
OL,10,F(OCGs) operating out of retail
OL,11,Fpremises on their local high streets.
OL,13,FThere was also "almost universal
OL,14,Frecognition" ` involving 99% of
OL,15,Fofficers ` that Trading Standards had
OL,16,Fseen an increase in the number of cash-
OL,17,Fintensive businesses opening on their
OL,18,Flocal high streets since 2020.
OL,26,@uD@POUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777558269
OL,3,C'Dodgy shops' surge across UK as vape
OL,4,Cand convenience stores tied to crime
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FAlmost three-quarters of Trading
OL,8,FStandards professionals (72%) reported
OL,9,Fexperiencing intimidatory behaviour or
OL,10,Fhad been threatened with violence in
OL,11,Fthe course of their duties.
OL,13,FIt said the budgets of Local Authority
OL,14,FTrading Standards (LATS) services had
OL,15,Fbeen cut by up to 50% over the last
OL,16,Fdecade, with staffing stripped to
OL,17,Fminimum levels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777558269
OL,3,C'Dodgy shops' surge across UK as vape
OL,4,Cand convenience stores tied to crime
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FTrading Standards warned that this `
OL,8,Fcoupled with resource "challenges" for
OL,9,Fother key enforcement agencies,
OL,10,Fincluding police ` had coincided with
OL,11,Fthe rapid spread of dodgy shops across
OL,12,Fthe UK, as well as complex criminal
OL,13,Fnetworks that underpinned them.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
