CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777558269
OL,3,C'Dodgy shops' surge across UK as vape
OL,4,Cand convenience stores tied to crime
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FThe report outlined a 10-point plan to
OL,8,F"reclaim the UK's high streets",
OL,9,Fincluding investing in Trading
OL,10,FStandards, making the sale of illegal
OL,11,Fgoods a trigger for licence review,
OL,12,Fand an additional #20 million to
OL,13,Fbolster Trading Standards resources
OL,14,Ffor ports and borders.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777558269
OL,3,C'Dodgy shops' surge across UK as vape
OL,4,Cand convenience stores tied to crime
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FJohn Herriman, chief executive of the
OL,8,FChartered Trading Standards Institute
OL,9,F(CTSI), said: "It is clear from this
OL,10,Fresearch that serious and organised
OL,11,Fcrime is endemic across the UK, and
OL,12,Fthe threat posed by illegitimate high
OL,13,Fstreet businesses is having a
OL,14,Fsignificant impact on the work of
OL,15,FTrading Standards, and our ability to
OL,16,Fprotect consumers and maintain the
OL,17,Flevel playing field for legitimate
OL,18,Fbusiness."
OL,26,@qD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
