OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777558269
OL,3,C'Dodgy shops' surge across UK as vape
OL,4,Cand convenience stores tied to crime
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FThese shops often brought with them
OL,8,Fassociated criminality including anti-
OL,9,Fsocial behaviour, theft and violent
OL,10,Fcrime, drug supply, modern slavery,
OL,11,Fand child sexual exploitation.
OL,13,FEd Woodall, chief executive of the
OL,14,FAssociation of Convenience Stores,
OL,15,Fsaid responsible convenience retailers
OL,16,Fwere "extremely frustrated" with rogue
OL,17,Ftraders operating with impunity in
OL,18,Ftheir local area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777558269
OL,3,C'Dodgy shops' surge across UK as vape
OL,4,Cand convenience stores tied to crime
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,F"Tens of millions of pounds need to be
OL,8,Finvested in local enforcement capacity
OL,9,Fto shut down these rogue traders and
OL,10,Fsupport the responsible retailers that
OL,11,Fare suffering as a result," he said.
OL,13,FSimilarly, the Independent Vape Trade
OL,14,FAssociation said the rogue traders and
OL,15,Fcriminals have damaged the public's
OL,16,Funderstanding of the vape sector, with
OL,17,Flaw-abiding vape businesses suffering
OL,18,Fthe consequences.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
