CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777558269
OL,3,C'Dodgy shops' surge across UK as vape
OL,4,Cand convenience stores tied to crime
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FIts chief executive, Gillian Golden,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We fully endorse their 10-point
OL,9,Fplan."
OL,11,F"We have already seen where greater
OL,12,Finter-agency working to tackle
OL,13,Forganised crime has been successful.
OL,14,FIt would be an even greater win for
OL,15,Flegitimate businesses and consumers if
OL,16,Fthe Government takes forward these
OL,17,Frecommendations," he added.
OL,26,@pD@GOUsD@AOUyD@QO]
